---
source: src/cli/mod.rs
assertion: curate retire writes audited retirement record without deletion
schema:
  response: ee.response.v1
  retire: ee.curate.retire.v1
contracts:
  - retire writes an audited state transition without deleting the candidate
  - dry-run preview reports what would be retired
  - missing candidate returns NotFound with repair hint
  - actor recorded in audit metadata when provided
  - reason recorded in audit trail
  - JSON stdout is ee.response.v1 envelope
evidence:
  - CurateRetireArgs.candidate_id
  - CurateRetireArgs.dry_run
  - CurateRetireArgs.actor
  - CurateRetireArgs.reason
  - CurateRetireReport.schema
  - CurateRetireReport.from_status
  - CurateRetireReport.to_status
  - CurateRetireReport.audit_id
